Portland, Maine Tides

About this website

This is a simple mobile-focused website (and progressive web app) for checking the current tide levels in the Casco Bay region of maine. The tide data comes from rtide https://github.com/poissonconsulting/rtide and the NOAA. Weather data comes from Open Weather Map https://openweathermap.org.

You can add the "app" to your phone home screen by selecting "add to home screen" in Sarafi (iPhone) or Chrome (Android).

Not a web-developer, just a tinkerer who likes taking the dogs to the beach. code
